  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Manufacturing OPERATOR",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Operate advanced cleanroom manufacturing equipment with precision and care.</p></li><li><p>Conduct detailed visual inspections to ensure the highest product quality.</p></li><li><p>Safely handle, prepare, and load materials into the production process.</p></li><li><p>Maintain an exceptionally clean, organized, and efficient workstation daily.</p></li><li><p>Identify and promptly report any equipment issues or process irregularities.</p></li><li><p>Follow all documented procedures and safety protocols without exception.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>Day Shift:</strong> 7:30 AM – 7:30 PM</p></li><li><p><strong>Night Shift:</strong> 7:30 PM – 7:30 AM</p></li><li><p><strong>Breaks:</strong> Each shift includes 2 paid tea breaks and a full-hour lunch break.</p></li><li><p><strong>Earn More:</strong> Optional overtime is regularly available to boost your income.<br /></p><ul><li><p><strong>Base Salary:</strong> $2,500 – $3,300/month (based on experience)</p></li><li><p><strong>Extra Earnings:</strong> Night shift allowance (up to $25/night) + overtime pay</p></li><li><p><strong>Annual Rewards:</strong> 13th-month salary + performance bonus (typically 1–2 months)</p></li></ul></li></ul><p><br /><br /></p><p><br /><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
